sourceMeaningMnemonic: The <radical>moon</radical> grants a <radical>gladiator</radical> its <radical>power</radical> so he will <kanji>win</kanji>! <kanji>Victory</kanji> will be his!
meaningInfo: Watch as the moon's power fills the gladiator. He starts to glow, grows larger, and has some craters on his face now. Well.. okay.
readingMnemonic: He <kanji>win</kanji>s over and over again, and soon the <reading>Shou</reading>gun (<ja>しょう</ja>) is even rooting for him. In fact, the Shougun claims him as his personal gladiator of choice.
readingInfo: The Shougun is only interested in people who win. But you probably could have guessed that already.
